title: High Gender Equality Rating
description: In 2023, Kyrgyzstan achieved a CPIA gender equality rating of 4.5, indicating a strong commitment to gender equality compared to other nations.

title: Excellent Urban Handwashing Facilities
description: As of 2019, 98.66% of Kyrgyzstan's urban population had access to basic handwashing facilities, showcasing the country's focus on urban hygiene.

title: Widespread Handwashing Access
description: In 2019, 98.28% of Kyrgyzstan's total population had access to basic handwashing facilities, reflecting a strong national emphasis on hygiene.

title: Minimal Aid from Luxembourg
description: In 2015, Kyrgyzstan received a minimal net bilateral aid flow of $9,999.99 from Luxembourg, indicating limited financial support from this donor.
